ProcessBuilder processBuilder = new ProcessBuilder(
    "mv",
    "/path/with/single'quote.txt",     // source
    "/target/path/with'single.txt"     // destination
);
processBuilder.inheritIO(); // optional, to show output/errors
Process process = processBuilder.start();
int exitCode = process.waitFor();
System.out.println("Exited with code: " + exitCode);

This avoids problems with single quotes, spaces, and other special characters 
because each argument is passed directly without shell interpretation.
